# Performance Optimization Guidelines
- Use React.memo for pure function components
- Implement lazy loading for route components
- Optimize useEffect dependencies to prevent unnecessary re-renders

# Testing Requirements
- Write unit tests using Jest and React Testing Library
- Ensure at least 80% test coverage
- Use snapshot testing for UI components

# Documentation Standards
- Write comments for functions and components using JSDoc format
- Include PropTypes validation in components
- Each major directory must contain a README.md file in both English and Chinese

# Error Handling Preferences
- Use try/catch blocks for asynchronous operations
- Implement a global error boundary component